body.name: 69" Tall Heavy-Duty Bookshelf, 5-Tier Metal Bookshelf with Adjustable Shelves, Open Shelf Bookcase, Tall Bookshelf for Home Office, Library, Bedroom, Including Book Stopper
features: 【Durable & Sturdy Construction】- Crafted from robust all-metal materials, the 5-Tier heavy-duty metal bookshelf is designed to provide strength and stability in book storage. Each shelf has a load-bearing capacity of 280lbs, exceeding expectations for heavy-duty storage.

【Flexible & Adjustable】- Effortlessly adjust the height of each shelf to accommodate your growing book collection. This feature allows for a well-organized and easily accessible library, making the white bookshelf an ideal choice for those who value both form and function.

【Unique Design】- The metal bookshelf boasts a stylish appearance and sturdy frame, with a unique book stopper design. The book stoppers effectively prevent books from falling off the shelves, keeping them organized and in place. Additionally, the white bookshelf comes with an anti-tilt device, providing both style and functionality.

【Easy Assembly】- No need for complicated tools or extensive DIY skills. The metal bookcase requires no screws for assembly, making it easy for anyone to install. Simply follow the included instructions, and you'll have your new metal bookshelf up and running in no time.

【Stylish & Sleek Design】- With its clean lines and all-metal construction, the modern and minimalist design of this metal bookshelf adds a touch of sophistication to any room. It is a perfect addition to any home or office space, providing both style and functionality.
body.description: Introducing the OSEILLC 5-Tier Metal Bookshelf with Adjustable Storage Shelves, a heavy-duty and durable book storage solution for your home, office, or library. Crafted from robust all-metal materials, this bookshelf is designed to stand the test of time, providing strength and stability for your book collection. Each shelf has a remarkable load-bearing capacity, with the ability to hold up to 280lbs. This means you can confidently store your books, whether you have a few favorites or an extensive collection. One of the standout features of this metal bookshelf is its flexibility and adjustability. You can effortlessly adjust the height of each of the five shelves to accommodate your growing collection. This allows you to create a well-organized and easily accessible library, ensuring you can find your favorite books with ease. In addition to its functionality, this metal bookshelf also boasts a unique design. It features book stoppers that effectively prevent books from falling off the shelves. This keeps your books organized and in place, reducing clutter. The bookshelf also comes with an anti-tilt device, providing added stability and safety. Assembling this metal bookshelf is a breeze. No need for complicated tools or extensive DIY skills. The bookshelf requires no screws for assembly, making it easy for anyone to install. Simply follow the included instructions, and you'll have your new bookshelf up and running in no time. Apart from its practicality, this metal bookshelf also adds a touch of style and sophistication. Its modern and minimalist design, with clean lines and all-metal construction, complements any room decor. Whether you place it in your living room, bedroom, office, or library, it adds a sleek and stylish element to the space. Overall, the OSEILLC 5-Tier Metal Bookshelf with Adjustable Storage Shelves is the perfect choice for those who demand both strength and style in their book storage solution. Get yours today and enjoy a well-organized and visually appealing library experience.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and Easy To Assemble
reviews.reviewText: One of the easiest pieces of furniture I've ever assembled. It does not have nuts or bolts, every thing just slides in place. The shelves themself have a little bit of play, but it feels sturdy and I loaded it with a bunch of textbooks. I'm buying a second one now because I underestimated how many books I have.
